\c 23
\s Impendulo kaJobe: Ufisa ukulandisa udaba lwakhe phambi kukaNkulunkulu
\p
\v 1 Wasephendula uJobe wathi:
\p
\v 2 Lalamuhla\x + Zek. 9.12.\x* isikhalazo sami silokubaba\x + 21.4.\x*; isandla sami sinzima phezu kokububula kwami.
\v 3 Kungathi ngabe ngiyazi lapho engingamthola khona\x + 13.3. 16.21.\x*! Bengingeza enkundleni yakhe\x + Hez. 43.11. Nah. 2.9.\x*!
\v 4 Ngibeke kuhle udaba \add lwami\add* phambi kwakhe\x + 13.18.\x*, ngigcwalise umlomo wami ngokuphikisa\x + 13.6.\x*.
\v 5 Bengingawazi amazwi azangiphendula ngawo, ngiqedisise azakutsho kimi.
\v 6 Uzaphikisana lami ngobukhulu bamandla yini? Hatshi, kodwa uzabeka \add inhliziyo yakhe\add* kimi\x + 30.18. 9.34. 13.21.\x*.
\v 7 Lapho oqotho angaphikisana laye; ngakho bengizaphepha phakade kumahluleli wami.
\v 8 Khangelani\x + 9.11.\x* ngiya phambili, kodwa kakho\x + 18.20.\x*, lemuva\x + 18.20.\x*, kodwa kangimboni\x + 9.11.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakwesokhohlo ekusebenzeni kwakhe, kodwa kangi\add m\add*boni\x + Gen. 14.15.\x*; uyacatsha ngakwesokunene\x + 1 Sam. 23.19.\x*, kodwa kangi\add m\add*boni\x + 9.11.\x*.
\v 10 Kanti uyayazi indlela elami\x + Hlab. 139.1-3.\x*; kangihlole, ngizaphuma njengegolide\x + Hlab. 17.3. 66.10. Jak. 1.12.\x*.
\v 11 Unyawo lwami lubambelele enyathelweni lakhe\x + Hlab. 44.18.\x*, ngiyigcinile indlela yakhe, kangiphambukanga\x + Hlab. 125.5.\x*.
\v 12 Kangisukanga lemlayweni wezindebe zakhe, ngawalondoloza amazwi omlomo wakhe okwedlula isabelo sami.
\v 13 Kodwa yena ukokukodwa, ngubani-ke ongambuyisela emuva\x + 9.12.\x*? Lokho umphefumulo wakhe okufisayo uyakwenza\x + Hlab. 115.3.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba uzaphelelisa engikumiselweyo; lezinto ezinengi ezinjalo zikuye\x + 10.13.\x*.
\v 15 Ngenxa yalokho ngitshaywa luvalo phambi kwakhe; ngicabanga, ngiyamesaba\x + Lilo 4.16.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba uNkulunkulu wenze inhliziyo yami yaphela amandla, loSomandla ungethusile\x + Dute. 20.3. Hlab. 22.14.\x*.
\v 17 Ngoba kangiqunywanga phambi komnyama\x + 17.12. 22.11.\x*, wagubuzela ubumnyama\x + 10.22.\x* ebusweni bami\x + 9.27.\x*.